'''邊疆書店'''（{{lang-en|'''Borderlands Books'''}}）是一家位於[[舊金山|舊金山]]的[[獨立書店|獨立書店]]，專門販售[[科幻|科幻]]、[[奇幻|奇幻]]、和恐怖類小說。1997年艾倫·彼茲（Alan Beatts）在Hayes Valley創立了這家店，起初只賣二手書籍，其中包含彼茲個人的收藏。<ref>Pickoff-White, Lisa. (April 2, 2008). [http://www.sfweekly.com/2008-04-02/culture/borderlands-helps-make-the-bay-area-a-sci-fi-bookstore-haven/ "Borderlands Helps Make the Bay Area a Sci-Fi Bookstore Haven"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfweekly.com/2008-04-02/culture/borderlands-helps-make-the-bay-area-a-sci-fi-bookstore-haven/ |date=20140408020310 }}. ''SF Weekly''. Retrieved December 29, 2011.</ref> 2001年書店遷移到如今位於Mission District的店面。<ref>[http://borderlands-books.com/about_history.html About the store: Store history] {{Wayback|url=http://borderlands-books.com/about_history.html |date=20100412054024 }}. Borderlands-books.com. Retrieved December 29, 2011.</ref> 

==历史==
2008年彼茲和書店經理裘德·費爾德曼（Jude Feldman）一同獲得[[世界奇幻獎|世界奇幻獎]]的職業人士特別貢獻獎。<ref>[http://www.worldfantasy.org/awards/2008.html/ "World Fantasy 2008 Award Recipients & Nominees"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201075150/http://worldfantasy.org/awards/2008.html |date=2010-12-01 }}. Worldfantasy.org. Retrieved October 22, 2011.</ref>2009年彼茲開設了書店的附屬咖啡館。<ref>Hernandez, Rigoberto (January 1, 2010). [http://missionlocal.org/2010/01/room-for-one-more-borderlands-cafe-opens/ "Move Over, Borderlands Opens Its Cafe on Valencia"] {{Wayback|url=http://missionlocal.org/2010/01/room-for-one-more-borderlands-cafe-opens/ |date=20210122092657 }}. ''Mission Local''.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/10/us/10bcomnivore.html|accessdate=2012-10-02|title=The Bay Citizen - Niche Bookstores Provide More Than Books|work=Bay Citizen|first=Reyhan|last=Harmanci|date=September 9, 2010|publisher=''The New York Times''|edition=National|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309111614/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/10/us/10bcomnivore.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

